<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #7E22CE; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background-color: #fff; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .message-box { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #7E22CE; margin: 20px 0; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #7E22CE; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; padding: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>MediVault Support</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= @user.first_name %>,</h2>

      <p>Our support team has replied to your message.</p>

      <div class="message-box">
        <p style="margin: 0; white-space: pre-wrap;"><%= @reply.message %></p>
      </div>

      <p>You can view the full conversation and reply by clicking the button below:</p>

      <a href="<%= @conversation_url %>" class="button">View Conversation</a>

      <p>If you have any additional questions, feel free to reply to the conversation.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>The MediVault Support Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent from an automated system. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
